<h1><i class="fa fa-home"></i>Sharing by Home Page</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-files"><i class="fa fa-share"></i>Sharing Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-home"></i>Sharing by Home Page</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> offers a simple way for you to share files and pictures on your <a href="#help/creating-profile/viewing-home-page">public home page</a>. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-folder"></i>Your Public Folder</h2
			<p>When you create your <%= application.name %> account, a set of standard folders is created for you in your home directory.  One of these folders is named "Public".  This folder is used to share items on your <a href="#help/creating-profile/viewing-home-page">public home page</a>.</p>

			<div class="icon-grid figure">
				<div class="directory item">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="icon"><img src="images/icons/folders/public-empty.svg" /></div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="name">Public</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-file"></i>Your Public Files</h2
			<p>When you move or copy files into your Public folder, they will become visible on the "Files" tab of your <a href="#help/creating-profile/viewing-home-page">public home page</a> for anyone to see.</p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-home-page/public-files.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Public Files Tab"><img src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-home-page/public-files.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Public Files Tab</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-camera"></i>Your Public Photos</h2
			<p>When you move or copy images into your Public folder, they will become visible on the "Photos" tab of your <a href="#help/creating-profile/viewing-home-page">public home page</a> for anyone to see.</p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-home-page/public-photos.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="Public Photos Tab"><img src="images/help/sharing-files/sharing-by-home-page/public-photos.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Public Photos Tab</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>